    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Stories with a Christmas, winter, or ghostly theme usually published to coincide with the Christmas season. A particulary Victorian publishing phenomenon.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>British English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
